  "title": "The Night of the Living Pumpkins",
  "description": "A horror resource pack set in a world invaded by living pumpkins.",
  "body": "<center> \n\n![The_Night_of_the_Living_Pumpkins_Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81d9b1a6cbd73212dafea52a4a79d1d116161047.png)\n\n\n_**In distant corners of the Minecraft world, <br>\nlegends tell of a night known as \"The Night of the Living Pumpkins\".**_\n\n<br>\nOnce every year, this night is dedicated to honoring those who have passed away. It is said that if the living forget to pay their respects, the spirits of the dead will rise, taking possession of the pumpkins in the fields and turning them into vengeful creatures eager to claim the souls of the ungrateful.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/zXHfboXcrFc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/pixelforge\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/32237a5eb0e69b0cfb6f79b09d08bafae2139664.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/shadows_pixelforge\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f8e5473c7cc891773d0963a204a7dbc0cae6ab8.png\" alt=\"Ko-fi\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/QrU6QCFj5r\"> \n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab1d9434d86f69f02be997775cc20d9f968fc6a6.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fc15ed1de151999554a0a966e39ccaef439d6d4d.png\" alt=\"Twitch\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2f10668a84476def0faf37c42319e0222484f94d.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/c/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b10f11429c9b97af2b45fcda64792d815fdeb5fb.png\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/shadowspixelforge/projects\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6aa1b4a7d469617ce0e922b931c24e73ef48dc59.png\" alt=\"Curseforge\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3qlCr9lXguH44qq5xqAlzQ\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/74af846b0dabfde51cc50f295809ec96f63e26a2.png\" alt=\"Youtube\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://x.com/SPixelForge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eb699f87a889d2710efc5dcff9b6b023b2be2d58.png\" alt=\"X\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a>\n<br><br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a8f40c7629034693eb5d2e696b36e4104b35b92.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a2f227dd350f4e2322f500900863b7a6696b74f7.png\" alt=\"NO DEPENDENCIES REQUIRED\" width=\"660\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n  **This resource pack works perfectly with Vanilla Minecraft - NO EXTRA MODS REQUIRED.** \n\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a8f40c7629034693eb5d2e696b36e4104b35b92.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c7f3b2837c699bc40bda584b7d5781389c4dbe3d.png\" alt=\"MORE INTERESTING PROJECTS\" width=\"690\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"20\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/shadows-pixels-reforged\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81c5b3f05c13dac83081221b58110365ada040c7_0.webp\" alt=\"Shadow's Pixels Reforged Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Shadow's Pixels Reforged\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/potion-recipes-pixels-reforged-edition!\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/543bdae3a809c8f18421b8c685cb5acf2ee52502.png\" alt=\"Potion Recipes: Pixels Reforged Edition Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Potion Recipes: <br> Pixels Reforged Edition\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/railbalance\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a3a7175ae8324de3de9cbfd3c3032780e5c9779a_0.webp\" alt=\"Railbalance Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Railbalance\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a8f40c7629034693eb5d2e696b36e4104b35b92.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f88863218a1c549051bc37c2cbd07a395d1bdd2.png\" alt=\"YOUR SUPPORT MAKES THE DIFFERENCE\" width=\"850\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\nIf you like the content I make, don’t hesitate to join my Patreon or Ko-fi to enjoy all the exclusive members-only content, you'll get access to a lot of bonus content like WIPs, making ofs, dev. blogs and much more!\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/shadows_pixelforge/tiers\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6dc8719629fd05f40aba4f4e58bc56458925abae.png\" alt=\"join ko-fi\" width=\"400\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/shadowspixelforge/membership\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e73a4a0852508cb8d2b6a3dae2a42baef09334c0.png\" alt=\"join patreon\" width=\"400\" height=\"50\"> </a> \n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a8f40c7629034693eb5d2e696b36e4104b35b92.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fb424f5c7e4031e9d8691616a446883413c75421.png\" alt=\"FAQs\" width=\"155\" height=\"50\">\n\n</center>\n<br>\n<br>\n\nHere I leave some answers to a few possible questions you may have, I hope it can help you.\n\n<details>\n  <summary>Frequently Asked Questions</summary>\n\n> **Q: Is The Night of the Living Pumpkins a Mod / Modpack / Data Pack / Plugin...?**\n> \n> A: No, The Night of the Living Pumpkins is just a resource pack and requires 0 dependencies, just Minecraft Vanilla!\n\n> **Q: Can you / Will you make a Bedrock port?**\n> \n> A: To make a version that would work on Bedrock, I would need to learn how Bedrock works. So that's not something I plan to do any time soon for now, but it will come eventually.\n\n> **Q: Do you / Will you ever make a Mod?**\n> \n> A: For now we are mostly working on resource packs, follow us on ko-fi or patreon to stay up to date.\n\n> **Q: Why some mobs didn't changed?**\n> \n> A: This resource pack will be getting annual updates around october, these updates wont come to bring huge changes or complete overhauls to the existing content, this is a small project to work and build through time, with small-mid size additions, so there will probably be something that if it didn't change this year, the next one probably be changing.\n\n> **Q: Can I put your Resource Pack in my Modpack?**\n> \n> A: Yes, you can do it as long as you give me credit.\n\n\n</details>",
